<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Ativação de Senha Vita Flow</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    /* Reset CSS */
    body,
    table,
    td,
    a {
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }

    table,
    td {
      mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
      mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
    }

    img {
      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      border: 0;
      height: auto;
      line-height: 100%;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a[x-apple-data-detectors] {
      color: inherit !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      font-size: inherit !important;
      font-family: inherit !important;
      font-weight: inherit !important;
      line-height: inherit !important;
    }

    /* Estilos Principais */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #F0F0F0;
    }

    .full-width {
      width: 100% !important;
    }

    .content-box {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .dark-bg {
      background-color: #2C2C2C;
    }

    .light-text {
      color: #F0F0F0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .bronze-highlight {
      color: #A39D7D;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F0F0F0;">

  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 0 10px;">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
          style="max-width: 600px; border-collapse: collapse;">

          <tr>
            <td align="center" class="dark-bg" style="padding: 30px 0 20px 0; background-color: #2C2C2C;">
              <img src="https://vitaflow-frontend.vercel.app/vitaflow.svg"
                alt="Vita Flow | Saúde personalizada, vida equilibrada" width="180"
                style="display: block; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #F0F0F0; font-size: 18px;">
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td align="center" class="dark-bg" style="padding: 40px 30px 40px 30px; background-color: #2C2C2C;">
              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">

                <tr>
                  <td align="left" class="light-text"
                    style="padding-bottom: 20px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px; font-weight: bold;">
                    Olá, {{name}}
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td align="left" class="light-text" style="padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
                    Você solicitou a redefinição da sua senha na **Vita Flow**. Para prosseguir e criar uma nova senha,
                    por favor, clique no botão abaixo.
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                    <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: #A39D7D;">
                          <a href="{{resetLink}}" target="_blank"
                            style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #2C2C2C; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #A39D7D; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
                            REDEFINIR SENHA
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td align="center" class="light-text"
                    style="padding-top: 10px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: #CCCCCC;">
                    Se o botão não funcionar, copie e cole o seguinte link em seu navegador:<br>
                    <a href="{{resetLink}}" target="_blank" class="bronze-highlight"
                      style="color: #2C2C2C; word-break: break-all; text-decoration: underline;">{{resetLink}}</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                  <td align="left" class="light-text" style="padding-top: 30px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;">
                    ** Importante: ** Se você não solicitou essa redefinição, por favor, ignore este e-mail. Sua senha
                    permanecerá a mesma.
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td align="center" class="dark-bg"
              style="padding: 20px 30px 30px 30px; background-color: #2C2C2C; border-top: 1px solid #A39D7D;">
              <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" class="light-text" style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: #CCCCCC;">
                    Em caso de dúvidas, responda a este e-mail.<br>
                    Atenciosamente,<br>
                    <span class="bronze-highlight" style="font-weight: bold;">A Equipe Vita Flow</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>